						<SPAN CLASS="txtP"><SPAN CLASS="txtH2">About Us</SPAN><br>
							<br>
							TellSafe, LLC is a privately held independent company established in 2003. 
							TellSafe's Compliant™ service gives your employees access to anonymous 
							reporting 24 hours a day, every day of the year.<br>
							<br>
							Employees can send reports by visiting our website, calling our toll-free 
							number, using a courier service or the U.S postal service. Our encryption 
							procedures ensure the anonymity of employees who make reports.<br>
							<br>
							<br>
							<SPAN CLASS="txtH2">Management Profile</SPAN><br>
							<br>
							<SPAN CLASS="txtH1">Bart A. Lewin</SPAN> (<A HREF="mailto:blewin@tellsafe.com">blewin@tellsafe.com</A>)<br>
							Mr. Lewin has been working in the field of Information Technology since 1980, 
							concentrating on marketing technology since 1987. He has held executive 
							technical management positions at Chevron Chemical Company (NYSE: CHV) and 
							International Gaming Technology (NYSE: IGT) where he developed the first equity 
							based rewards program for slot players. He founded a successful database 
							marketing software company (DataDesigns, Inc.) in 1990. DataDesigns was 
							eventually acquired by Group 1 Software (NASDAQ: GSOF) in 1995. Mr. Lewin holds 
							a Bachelor of Arts degree from Reed College and has received additional 
							training at the University of California, the University of Kyoto and the 
							University of Oxford.<br>
							<br>
